graph LR
    Feast[Feast Feature Store<br/>Operator + Servers]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -->|operator runtime| Go[Go 1.22+]
    Feast -->|server runtime| Python[Python 3.11]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Feast -.->|persistent storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    Feast -.->|high-perf online store| Redis[Redis 5.0+]
    Feast -.->|offline data storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    Feast -.->|enhanced platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.17+]

    %% Internal RHOAI/ODH Dependencies
    Feast -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Feast -->|notebook integration| KubeflowNB[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Feast -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Feast -.->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth / OIDC]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[RHOAI Dashboard] -.->|feature store mgmt UI| Feast
    Notebooks[Data Science Notebooks] -->|feast SDK| Feast
    Pipelines[ML Pipelines] -->|feature retrieval| Feast
    ModelServing[Model Serving<br/>KServe/ModelMesh] -->|online features| Feast
    Training[Training Jobs] -->|historical features| Feast

    %% External Services
    Feast -.->|feature sync| Git[Git Repository]
    Feast -->|API server| KubeAPI[Kubernetes API]

    %% Component legend
    subgraph Legend
        Required[Required Dependency]
        Optional[Optional Dependency]
        Integration[Integration Point]
    end

    %% Styling
    style Feast fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
